Wow, this is a supporting point to establish training people to get them out of your hair?  You've got some serious issues there, pillowbiter.  Might want to pull that fence post out of your ass and consider that this kind of BS isn't tolerated in three spheres of an EQ player's life on the tribunal:<br>
