2) The Tribunal Community - We don't tolerate bullshit from pieces of monkey shit, hence the sticky thread at the top.<br>
3) PnP - Camp disputes are settled by a guide if people can't get along.  Training gets you warnings, suspensions, or a banning.  Which is the non-acceptable one for you?<br>
